# TCGA/GDC download caches (can be 2+ GB)
**/data_in/GDCdata/
**/data_in/*.rds

# 10x Genomics unpacked cellranger output (raw input, regenerable)
**/data_in/filtered_gene_bc_matrices/
**/data_in/*.mtx
**/data_in/*.tsv

# Large intermediate RDS files
**/data_out/rds/*.rds

